Biggest Insight

I realized that having a structured roadmap makes career goals much more achievable. Breaking a long-term goal into smaller milestones helps me focus on what to learn and when.

Learnings

- Learned how Chain-of-Thought prompting improves output quality.
- Learned how structured questioning leads to better AI responses.
- Learned how to create a career roadmap using AI.

Observations

- The roadmap was personalized.
- The output was more detailed than a normal prompt.
- Breaking problems into steps improved the response quality.

